name: Malaysian Virgin Hair
description:
Textures: Straight, Body Wave, And Ocean Wave

100% Pure Virgin Malaysian Hair for sew-in weaves. This hair is in its pure and natural state, no chemical processing or coloring. This hair is very durable, minimal to no shedding, and tangle-free. With proper maintenance it will be long lasting and reusable. Hair can be curled, flat ironed, colored and permed just like your own hair.

Color: Natural Brown which is equal to a 1B

One Bundle=3.5-4 oz
Suggested that you order 3 bundles for lengths 12-24 inches and 4 bundles for lengths longer than 24 inches a full install!

**PRICE IS FOR ONE BUNDLE**
